title: Northern Soul ~ Cleethorpes Pier Shufflers
description:
NorthernSoul &#039;Cleethorpes&#039; by  unionjack 

I have been around the Northern Soul scene for many years ~ promoting, Dj, and total freak. I have put together a few tracks that I associate with Cleethorpes. Some of which were borrowed from many orher fans to whom I say thank you very much guys ( Keep the Faith ).
You might say &#039; but I used to hear this played at such n such a place &#039;, obviously there was a big crossover, with the likes of Willie Mitchells &#039;The Driving Beat&#039; being played at everywhere from the Torch to the 6t&#039;s night in West Hampstead or the haunting sounds of The Dynatones, where I dare you to stay in your seats. And classic Cleethorpes like The Crows &#039;Autumn of Your Tomorrow&#039; and Susan Colemans &#039;The Age of the Wolf&#039; ,Spooky n Sue,Rain,Hosana Hipit, The Baby sitters ~ OMG Ive just had tingles!! But this torrent is MY OWN personal point of view and as they are all great tracks who really cares. 
All I need for you to do now is to enjoy it but please seed it also ~ we need to keep these rarities alive.
